QuestData.Title: Meet with Kazak Darkscream
QuestData.Description: I have just received word from Kazak Darkscream, Orgrimmar's foremost warlock trainer. He wishes you to travel to Orgrimmar and speak with him at The Barracks in the Valley of Honor. It sounds like he has an important mission for you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Kazak Darkscream at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Kazak Darkscream at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
